    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class High5IPS
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    The main class that controls the application. The High-5 Image Processing System allows a user to select their own images and edit them them by adding different effects to the images. This is an unfinished Alpha release.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Team High Five
